description: Try our easy to follow Meat & Veggie Kebabs recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Skewer & kebab,Zucchini,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Tomato,Low sugar,Mushroom,Peanut free
name: Meat & Veggie Kebabs Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Line a baking tray with baking paper.
Thread a bamboo skewer with a tomato, meatball, mushroom half, another meatball and finish with zucchini. Repeat with remaining meatballs and vegetables. Arrange on tray.
Spray well with oil. Cook for 15 minutes, turning halfway through cooking time, until meatballs are cooked through. Serve.
